		"Name": "Jotunn",
		"Details": "Originally designed by Vandenburg Mechanized Industries on New Vandenburg in the Taurian Concordat, the Jotunn would quickly be inducted in the Drone Cockpit program as a support mech for the newly upgraded TDF forces.  The base TSL test platform has multiple Artillery hardpoints to support various configurations in helping to decide what is the final production loadout for artillery mechs.  Given the importance of combat testing it was decided to outfit the prototype JTN-4TSL with enhanced defensive measures, ones that drove costs up and slowed production but provided better staying power on the field.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>Pafftek Industries Sub-mod</color></b>",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_jotunn"
	},
